                      "text": "过场动画与预告",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "3.3版本PV：「六入尽明，诸相皆无」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/10/142453215/308a556a3922c31a6eb39f4939d991a3_8623706935925513938.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2022年11月25日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "稻妻自古以来就不缺少怪谈传说。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "有些自然与世代传承的鬼怪大妖脱不了干系；",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "而有些，也许只是旧时遗事的苍凉一角…",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube：",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "剧情PV-「秋津羽戏」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/05/142453215/e418ce0df87e907a51be41dc89c21568_5686981907590565404.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2022年12月19日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "简单来说，以羽子板击球打靶，考验速度、耐性与方向控制力，即为「秋津羽戏」。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "此番游艺可以单人玩耍，但若想合作或比试，可要找个默契的同伴才能尽兴。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube：",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "5.4版本PV：「梦间见月明」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/07/142453215/9b343d2594fb3fba2a4551796b6e6991_1865611233134467642.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2025年1月24日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "人生就像穿梭在美梦与噩梦之间。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "感觉到紧张、恐惧、无法喘息的时刻，",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "请稍作休息，品尝美梦的甘甜，",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "并将噩梦揉碎咀嚼。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Youtube：",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
